{"tid":2284525,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"8.31晩上用傘襲兩警 設計師罪成囚4個月","createTime":"2020-11-13T10:59:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T16:29:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c12ee2c41519c361cb0871b574c0195791f94ee3","tid":2284525,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T10:59:30.000Z","msg":"去年8月31日晚上多區發生衝突，24歲設計師被指翌日凌晨在坑口港鐵站外以傘襲擊總督察及警署警長。審訊揭露涉案警署警長曾於另一宗反修例案中被裁定為不可靠證人，又以「唔想claim OT」為由解釋放工後仍在落口供的不合理紀錄。最終設計師今仍被裁定兩項襲警罪名成立。主任裁判官徐綺薇判刑時指案情嚴重，而當時有示威者聚集叫囂，襲擊行為有機會鼓勵附近人士一齊加入，屬不可忽略的風險，即時判囚4個月，但批准被告以1萬元保釋等候就定罪提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201113/YOS2FQKX6ZGZ5ASUT7WUYU43TE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201113%2FYOS2FQKX6ZGZ5ASUT7WUYU43TE%2F&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIoDkkQuUBcdRTUhzZaMUkok%3D&h=17641550\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201113%2FYOS2FQKX6ZGZ5ASUT7WUYU43TE%2F&h=dbad99c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201113/YOS2FQKX6ZGZ5ASUT7WUYU43TE/</a>"},{"pid":"a0661aae74588db7039a8ea3ba9443cc20e2f9fb","tid":2284525,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9846e7eced1556303b8ca1064a211f7c6104c17a","tid":2284525,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:00:36.000Z","msg":"辯方在審訊中稱，兩名警員錯誤辯認在包圍下走投無路、束手就擒的被告，身份辨認是案中爭議。辯方並提醒法庭，警署警長林華平在另一宗案件中曾被法官批評為不可靠證人。惟徐官裁決時指，每宗案件需獨立個別考慮，不可一概而論。<br />\n<br />\n徐官接納兩名警方證人誠實可靠，如實交待當日案發經過。雖然在多個環節有所出入，例如案發前曾有一女子跌到，總督察欲上前攙扶，而警署警長卻稱看不見；不過徐官認為，當時有大量人群聚集叫囂，警員作出驅散行動，在此環境下，兩名證人的專注在不同事務，實不出奇。<br />\n<br />\n另外，兩人在追截被告過程時距離不一，法庭認為每人對正常步速有不同標準，不同階段步伐亦會改變，因此認為辯方的批評不成立。"},{"pid":"bfbf972e186c01fecc454f4e3e5657bddd3d51cb","tid":2284525,"uid":301050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:02:07.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"4fe71c6949527c09decc678abc7705a7a65f718f","tid":2284525,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁都入"},{"pid":"2c66069cbd79d39c0f573c892ac39b836a704953","tid":2284525,"uid":92448,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T12:05:39.000Z","msg":"黑警+狗官+太監=港共曱甴集團"},{"pid":"9f3b4ca60a9e08f5b0c230bdd8e802d4ccd14863","tid":2284525,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T12:12:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096f43c69d5c38f8197ffd7373e6ffce84ebc928","tid":2284525,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T12:19:06.000Z","msg":"狗官<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27ab9216319f4a81a059a32297a46cf7d3ad7a4","tid":2284525,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T12:20:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0572de0928150f6cf184c551b1e9c4151b5406f8","tid":2284525,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T13:24:37.000Z","msg":"邊個話徐綺薇唔係紅官<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9024cbdcff5c5c2d1ab79020915ac472afe100","tid":2284525,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T13:25:39.000Z","msg":"徐官接納兩名警方證人誠實可靠，如實交待當日案發經過。<span class=\"red\">雖然在多個環節有所出入</span>"},{"pid":"1673254efeb25d901bddd1324cacedff530195fd","tid":2284525,"uid":322130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T13:26:46.000Z","msg":"正卜街，又鳩告"},{"pid":"5c8c17d2f1861c124c14647b2eebc5c56088ad59","tid":2284525,"uid":151469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":